      "span_text": "Despite initial findings that SLC35F3 is involved in thiamine transport, we do not yet understand the details of such action, including the affinity, capacity, and selectivity of SLC35F3 for its thiamine substrate; nor have we examined the effect of thiamine replacement upon BP or its precursor traits, though previous work in experimental animals  and humans (48) suggests a beneficial effect.",
